        "URL": "data:text/html;charset=utf-8,%3C!doctype%20html%3E%0A%3Chtml%20lang%3D%22%22%3E%0A%3Chead%3E%0A%20%20%3Cmeta%20charset%3D%22utf-8%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctitle%3EOur%20Position%20Against%20Suicide%3C%2Ftitle%3E%0A%3C%2Fhead%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%0A%3Cbody%20bgcolor%3D%22%23000000%22%20background%3D%22..%2Fimg%2Ftile.jpg%22%20text%3D%22%23ffccff%22%20link%3D%22%2300ff99%22%20vlink%3D%22%2366ccff%22%20alink%3D%22%23ff0066%22%3E%0A%3Chr%20width%3D%2298%25%22%20size%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cfont%20size%3D%227%22%20color%3D%22%23ff0099%22%3E%3Ccenter%3EOUR%20POSITION%20AGAINST%20SUICIDE%3C%2Fcenter%3E%0A%3C%2Ffont%3E%0A%3Chr%20width%3D%2298%25%22%20size%3D%221%22%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ccenter%3E%0A%3Ctable%20width%3D%2280%25%22%20border%3D%220%22%3E%0A%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%3Ctd%3E%0A%3Cimg%20align%3D%22left%22%20hspace%3D%2215%22%20alt%3D%22M20%2C%20the%20Trifid%20%0Anebula%20in%20Sagittarius%22%3E%0A%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%20color%3D%22%23ffccff%22%3E%0AWe%20know%20that%20it%20is%20only%20while%20we%20are%20in%20these%20physical%20vehicles%20(bodies)%20%0Athat%20we%20can%20learn%20the%20lessons%20needed%20to%20complete%20our%20own%20individual%20%0Atransition%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20complete%20our%20task%20of%20offering%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20%0AHeaven%20to%20this%20civilization%20one%20last%20time.%20%20We%20take%20good%20care%20of%20our%20vehicles%20%0Aso%20they%20can%20function%20well%20for%20us%20in%20this%20task%2C%20and%20we%20try%20to%20protect%20them%20%0Afrom%20any%20harm.%3Cp%3E%0A%0AWe%20fully%20desire%2C%20expect%2C%20and%20look%20forward%20to%20boarding%20a%20spacecraft%20from%20the%20%0ANext%20Level%20very%20soon%20(in%20our%20physical%20bodies).%20%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20in%20our%20%0Amind%20that%20our%20being%20%22picked%20up%22%20is%20inevitable%20in%20the%20very%20near%20future.%20%20But%20%0Awhat%20happens%20between%20now%20and%20then%20is%20the%20%3Cb%3Ebig%20question%3C%2Fb%3E.%20%20We%20are%20keenly%20%0Aaware%20of%20several%20possibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%0AIt%20could%20happen%20that%20before%20that%20spacecraft%20comes%2C%20one%20or%20more%20of%20us%20could%20%0Alose%20our%20physical%20vehicles%20(bodies)%20due%20to%20%22recall%2C%22%20accident%2C%20or%20at%20the%20%0Ahands%20of%20some%20irate%20individual.%20%20We%20do%20not%20anticipate%20this%2C%20but%20it%20is%20%0Apossible.%20%20Another%20possibility%20is%20that%2C%20because%20of%20the%20position%20we%20take%20in%20%0Aour%20information%2C%20we%20could%20find%20so%20much%20disfavor%20with%20the%20powers%20that%20control%20%0Athis%20world%20that%20there%20could%20be%20attempts%20to%20incarcerate%20us%20or%20to%20subject%20us%20%0Ato%20some%20sort%20of%20psychological%20or%20physical%20torture%20(such%20as%20occurred%20at%20both%20%0ARuby%20Ridge%20and%20Waco).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%0AIt%20has%20always%20been%20our%20way%20to%20examine%20all%20possibilities%2C%20and%20be%20mentally%20%0Aprepared%20for%20whatever%20may%20come%20our%20way.%20%20For%20example%2C%20consider%20what%20%0Ahappened%20at%20Masada%20around%2073%20A.D.%20%20A%20devout%20Jewish%20sect%2C%20after%20holding%20out%20%0Aagainst%20a%20siege%20by%20the%20Romans%2C%20to%20the%20best%20of%20their%20ability%2C%20and%20seeing%20%0Athat%20the%20murder%2C%20rape%2C%20and%20torture%20of%20their%20community%20was%20inevitable%2C%20%0Adetermined%20that%20it%20was%20permissible%20for%20them%20to%20evacuate%20their%20bodies%20by%20a%20%0Amore%20dignified%2C%20and%20less%20agonizing%20method.%20%20We%20have%20thoroughly%20discussed%20%0Athis%20topic%20(of%20willful%20exit%20of%20the%20body%20under%20such%20conditions)%2C%20and%20have%20%0Amentally%20prepared%20ourselves%20for%20this%20possibility%20(as%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20a%20few%20%0Aof%20our%20statements).%20%20However%2C%20this%20act%20certainly%20does%20not%20need%20serious%20%0Aconsideration%20at%20this%20time%2C%20and%20hopefully%20will%20not%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%0AThe%20true%20meaning%20of%20%22suicide%22%20is%20%3Ci%3Eto%20turn%20against%20the%20Next%20Level%20when%20it%20%0Ais%20being%20offered%3C%2Fi%3E.%20%20In%20these%20last%20days%2C%20we%20are%20focused%20on%20two%20primary%20%0Atasks%3A%20one%20-%20of%20making%20a%20last%20attempt%20at%20telling%20the%20truth%20about%20how%20the%20%0ANext%20Level%20may%20be%20entered%20(our%20last%20effort%20at%20offering%20to%20individuals%20of%20%0Athis%20civilization%20the%20way%20to%20avoid%20%22suicide%22)%3B%20and%20two%20-%20taking%20advantage%20%0Aof%20the%20rare%20opportunity%20we%20have%20each%20day%20-%20to%20work%20individually%20on%20our%20%0Apersonal%20overcoming%20and%20change%2C%20in%20preparation%20for%20entering%20the%20Kingdom%20%0Aof%20Heaven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffont%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cfont%20size%3D%224%22%20color%3D%22%23ffccff%22%3E%0A%3C%2Ffont%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3C%2Fcenter%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ccenter%3E%3Cimg%3E%3C%2Fcenter%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ccenter%3E%3Cimg%3E%3C%2Fcenter%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Ccenter%3E%0AFor%20the%20next%20topic%20on%20our%20list%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22member.htm%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%0AHow%20a%20Member%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven%20Might%20Appear%20%3Cstrong%3E%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3Cbr%3E%0AFor%20subsequent%20topics%20return%20to%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22..%2Findex.html%23keys%22%3E%0A%3Cstrong%3E%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Home%20Page%20Bookmarks%20%3Cstrong%3E%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%0ATo%20Access%20Our%20Online%20Book%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22..%2Fbook%2Fbook.htm%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%0AHow%20and%20When%20HEAVEN'S%20GATE%20May%20Be%20Entered%20%3Cstrong%3E%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%0A%3Cp%3E%0ATo%20Send%20Us%20an%20Email%20Use%3Cstrong%3E%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26nbsp%3B%0A%3Ca%20href%3D%22mailto%3Arep%40heavensgate.com%22%3E%20%0Arep%40heavensgate.com%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fcenter%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml